item.title: Trails
item.description: Trails Rearrange methods order on markdown file. 1. cartolastd - 696 observations - 19 timesteps - 17 dimensions - 5 classes ... The dataset was scrapped from the Brazilian fantasy soccer platform Cartola and represents the second turn of the 2017 championship. The scrapper source can be found at https://github.com/henriquepgomide/caRtola. To make the dataset smoother, the dimensions were cumulatively averaged. 2.
